    "We eval-uate a higher compression rate of p = 90% at the 7th layer in Table1.",
    "Larger compression rate allows the model to process more frames, but it comes with a significant performance drop.",
    "Comparing rows 4 and 5, after increasing compression rate from 50% to 90%, the accuracy on VideoMME decreases from 56.7 to 53.4.",
    "Impact of different LLM backbones under identical training recipe.",
    "To isolate the effect of model architecture from scaling up, we train a Transformer-based baseline using Qwen2.5 following exactly the same training recipe as our hybrid model."
